OL,7,F"I've lost my daughter. Why should he
OL,8,Fhave that choice of whether it should
OL,9,Fbe tested or not?" says Claire Reynolds
OL,11,FSharlotte's mother, Claire Reynolds is
OL,12,Fnow calling for a change in the law
OL,13,Fand wants the control taken out of a
OL,14,Fsuspect's hands.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said: "I was
OL,17,Fshocked. I've lost my daughter. Why
OL,18,Fshould he have that choice of whether
OL,19,Fit should be tested or not?"
