OL,7,FHe told the Commons: "The impact on
OL,8,Fthe local community is impossible to
OL,9,Funderestimate. I know friends of
OL,10,FSharlotte still fear crossing the road
OL,11,For walking to school by themselves, a
OL,12,Fmilestone any parent knows is an
OL,13,Fessential part of growing up.
