OL,7,F"I know parents who are so much more
OL,8,Fconcerned about their children going
OL,9,Fout to play because of the fear that
OL,10,Fthis could happen to their loved ones.
OL,11,FAnd as a father myself, I'm humbled
OL,12,Fevery time I work with Sharlotte's
OL,13,Fbrave and inspirational mother, Claire
OL,14,FReynolds."JThe Bill is due to be
OL,15,Fconsidered by the Commons again on 14
OL,16,FJune but is unlikely to become law
OL,17,Fwithout government support.
